description:
An add-on for ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN.
This set contains the following:

Playable Aircraft: ASF-X Shinden II
A cutting-edge support fighter built to handle a variety of situations.
Its two-tiered jet engine and variable forward-swept wings give this aircraft excellent versatility and flight stability. Its nickname is Shinden II.
This set also includes 7 skins, including the special Nagase skin.

This aircraft can equip the 6AAM, RKT, or LASM as its special weapon.
name: ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - ASF-X Shinden II Set
